{"tid":697802,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日終於搞到個上司一肚氣！","createTime":"2018-06-11T07:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T08:50:38.000Z","uid":50384,"like":5,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dfaea1777f14528b3ac456ec7e3e7104cca69366","tid":697802,"uid":50384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n話說我係公司成日比個上司屌我做野慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要周不時話我做錯，明明係上一手問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我好大怨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日終於忍唔住要爆了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我吃完個lunch返黎見到佢仲係自己房吃緊<br />\n我即刻去雪櫃到拎左罐汽水入房比佢飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我睇住佢飲左我先行返岀去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我企係房岀面聽住佢係咁係到嗝氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次仲唔到我搞到你一肚氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30204294192378536946164e5515c06555ee87fc","tid":697802,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:54:51.000Z","msg":"...?"},{"pid":"ccf15e130ba467a83f6ddcc6b064a72473e3f881","tid":697802,"uid":187956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:56:36.000Z","msg":"ching ho ball"},{"pid":"a068aedb5bce05e2f4d57e3dfbbcc6ec8eb86caf","tid":697802,"uid":12340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re